oofem.out
2D lattice tension on a 100x50 mm rectangle (Stage 6 MVP)
StaticStructural nsteps 1 nmodules 1 solverType "calm" rtolf 1.e-5 maxiter 10 steplength 1.e-5 minsteplength 1.e-5 hpcmode 2 hpc 2 2 1 hpcw 1 1.
errorcheck
domain 2dLattice
OutputManager tstep_all dofman_output { #@CTL1 #@CTL2 }
ncrosssect 1 nmat 1 nbc 2 nic 0 nltf 1 nset 2
latticecs 1 material 1
latticedamage 1 d 0 talpha 0. e 30.e9 e0 100.e-6 wf 100.e-4 coh 2. ec 10. stype 1
BoundaryCondition 1 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 3 1 2 6 values 3 0. 0. 0. set 1
BoundaryCondition 2 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 3 1 2 6 values 3 1.e-4 0. 0. set 2
ConstantFunction 1 f(t) 1.
Set 1 nodes 1 #@CTL1
Set 2 nodes 1 #@CTL2
#@grid 2dSM
#@mesher qhull
#@diam 0.008
#@perflag 2 0 0
#@thickness 1.0
#@rect 1 box 4 0. 0. 0.10 0.05
#@controlvertex 1 coords 2 0.0  0.025
#@controlvertex 2 coords 2 0.10 0.025
